t1-function.time-sleep-until-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link sleep()} - 延缓执行</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link usleep()} - 以指定的微秒数延迟执行</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link time_nanosleep()} - 延缓执行若干秒和纳秒</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link set_time_limit()} - 设置脚本最大执行时间</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
